**Note on plan-проспект**: The compound "план-проспект" is not in VESUM as a single lemma, but component forms "план" and "проспект" are both valid. The compound is standard in Ukrainian academic terminology (cf. Grade 11 textbooks on реферат writing). Use with a hyphen as taught in textbooks.

**Note on дослід vs. дослідження**: Both are VESUM-confirmed nouns. The false-friend distinction (дослід = experiment/lab test; дослідження = research/study) is a priority error-correction item for B2 learners.

